http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/andhra-pradesh/FB-page-of-BJP%E2%80%99s-AP-unit-crosses-1-lakh-%E2%80%98likes%E2%80%99/article13978809.ece

The BJP State party has reached a major milestone on its Facebook page with the number of ‘likes’ crossing 100,000 on Saturday.Celebrating the occasion, party state general secretary J. Syam Kishore said it was good that social media sites were helping the political parties in keeping touch with the masses and expanding their presence. It was on July 26, 2015 that BJP State party launched its official Facebook page and website and they have since attracted the attention of people. At least four lakh people were watching the FB page every week and the number of regular visitors went past 1,00,000 in a short span.